            p.pb10.text-justify This E-Sign Policy and Disclosure (the “Disclosure”) from GrowthFountain Capital LLC (“GFC”, “we”  or “us,” ) applies to all communications between you and GFC.  The words “you” and “your” means you, the uniquely identifiable individual person who has registered, generated a log-in or otherwise created an account or user profile on the website operated by GFC that serves as a funding portal in connection with the offer and sale of securities (the “Platform”).   If you are using the Platform at any time in any manner as an employee, representative, promoter or agent for any business or entity, then you understand and agree that this Disclosure applies to such business or entity and that you are accepting these terms on behalf of yourself and such business or entity.  
                        
