                    u.font-weight-bold Scope of Your Consent.    
                    |  You agree that we may provide you with any communications relating to your use of the Platform in electronic format.  You further agree that any signatures communicated electronically communicated are enforceable and binding.  Your consent to receive electronic communications and participate in electronic transactions includes, but is not limited to, (a) all legal and regulatory communications, (b) notices, disclosures, authorizations or other communications about transactions that occur through the Platform, (c) inquiries, statements or other communications about your account or use of the Platform, (d) information, documentation, confirmations and other communications related to any purchase or sale of securities, (e) changes in the terms of your account, the Terms of Use or Privacy Policy, as available on the Platform, (f) any user agreements or amendments thereto, and (g) acknowledgements and contractual terms that relate to any offering listed on the Platform.  You understand and agree that this consent may cover information that we are required by law to provide to you in writing.
                li.pb10.text-justify
