                    |  We will not send you a paper copy of any Communication from us. You can obtain a paper copy of an electronic Communication by printing it yourself through your account on the Platform.  All Communications in either electronic or paper format from us to you will be considered “in writing.” You should print or download for your records this Disclosure and any other Communication that is important to you.
